function Cart() {
    const monsteraPrice = 8
    const ivyPrice = 10
    const flowerPrice = 15
    return ( <
        div >
        <
        h2 > Panier < /h2> <
        ul >
        <
        li > Monstera: { monsteraPrice }€ < /li> <
        li > Lierre: { ivyPrice }€ < /li> <
        li > Fleurs: { flowerPrice }€ < /li> < /
        ul >
        Total: { monsteraPrice + ivyPrice + flowerPrice }€ <
        /div>
    )
}

export default Cart
